== 製作 ==
2017年9月26日，[[东方梦工厂|东方梦工厂]]聘請{{le|奧黛麗·威爾斯|Audrey Wells}}撰寫劇本《飛奔去月球》，以重述中國經典神話<ref>{{Cite web|author=Nancy Tartaglione|title=Oriental DreamWorks Names Peilin Chou As CCO; Designs Robust Animation Slate|url=https://deadline.com/2017/09/oriental-dreamworks-peilin-chou-chief-creative-officer-new-animation-slate-master-of-none-everest-over-the-moon-china-1202177361/|date=2017-09-26|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=2019-08-08|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308042509/https://deadline.com/2017/09/oriental-dreamworks-peilin-chou-chief-creative-officer-new-animation-slate-master-of-none-everest-over-the-moon-china-1202177361/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年2月6日，[[Netflix|Netflix]]獲得該片的發行權，[[葛連·基恩|葛連·基恩]]被選為導演<ref name=“NetflixSlate”>{{Cite web|author=Amanda N'Duka|title=Glen Keane to Direct ‘Over The Moon’ Animation Film For Netflix & Pearl Studio|url=https://deadline.com/2018/02/glen-keane-over-the-moon-animation-film-netflix-pearl-studio-1202279339/|date=2018-02-06|website=Deadline Hollywood|access-date=2019-08-08|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126125824/https://deadline.com/2018/02/glen-keane-over-the-moon-animation-film-netflix-pearl-studio-1202279339/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來，{{le|約翰·卡爾斯|John Kahrs}}加入參與導演一職。然而，在此期間，威爾斯於2018年去世，這成為了她的遺作。配音陣容於2020年6月對外發表<ref name="Cast">{{Cite web|author=Nancy Tartaglione|title=‘Over The Moon’ Trailer: Netflix & Pearl Studio’s Animated Musical Adventure Reveals Voice Cast|url=https://deadline.com/video/over-the-moon-trailer-cast-ken-jeong-john-cho-sandra-oh-netflix-video/|date=2020-06-23|website=Deadline Hollywood|access-date=2020-06-23|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023043455/https://deadline.com/video/over-the-moon-trailer-cast-ken-jeong-john-cho-sandra-oh-netflix-video/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

動畫是由{{le|索尼圖形圖像|Sony Pictures Imageworks}}所製作，同時也處理片中[[传统动画|传统动画]]的部份<ref>{{Cite web|author=Drew Taylor|title=Netflix Reveals Details, Trailer for Upcoming Animated Musical ‘Over the Moon’|url=https://collider.com/over-the-moon-netflix-trailer-cast/|date=2020-06-23|website=Deadline Hollywood|access-date=2020-06-23|archive-date=2020-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201223222439/https://collider.com/over-the-moon-netflix-trailer-cast/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

